ssets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb513e3890d0f6c10774963489b15b40886bc1b7","tid":36743,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個中五中六都好似考過好多年試咁<br />\n歸納兩種<br />\n<br />\n1. 考試專家型<br />\n5** cut off 係___分<br />\n我喺校內一直都係幾多幾多分<br />\n我覺得讀呢科應該點點點<br />\n(下省一萬字標奇立異嘅讀書心得)<br />\n<br />\n2. 補習打手型<br />\n我補邊個邊個<br />\n由幾分變到宜家幾分咁<br />\n又教得幾好 乜乜叉叉考試Predict 我出到去會有___<br />\n<br />\n其實咁做除左你以為自己好撚型之外係百害而無一利<br />\n呢個世界無必贏嘅仗<br />\n除左你有幾多實力之餘 仲有講考運<br />\n出年出到地獄咁深你做幾多年pastpaper都死啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真正喺考試贏嘅人係嗰種永遠覺得自己未學夠未穩陣有個靚grade嘅人</span><br />\n<br />\n所謂學而後知不足，此之謂也。<br />\n<br />\n見過太多妄自菲薄 同 妄自尊大嘅人有感</blockquote><br />\n呢句真 dse 30分定係gpa 4.0ge fd都有 佢哋都係呢種心態 從來唔敢教人讀書 分享人德 因為佢地知自己有進步空間"},{"pid":"faa76c22d63d09c2d4c5b006182f051b02719dbc","tid":36743,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日討論cut off 都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n盡力考就得啦 知cut off代表你會咁啱高過cut off咩<br />\nPS: DSE考唔好仲有好多出路 睇開少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de545147541e2f58c705c97b12a5597f567ba099","tid":36743,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"好撚同意<br />\n利申 以前學校predict25分up最後得十幾分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家見到啲中學雞講自己想點點點入乜科就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12453c564b411e0c3dfa979e35c2cc54c232c9f","tid":36743,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"16DSE教畜pre 13分<br />\n而家做緊大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e82a8b6d17fef4f306fc7b45fc1aa01ca8c3c10","tid":36743,"uid":31413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愈溫愈覺得溫唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚大壓力呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方向正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀到好撚辛苦<br />\n做練習個陣唔明背後原理但問人又叫我唔好理咁多 唔會考咁深 <br />\n記住佢就係 真係好戇鳩<br />\n諗到好抓狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過成日都係咁我已經比佢地同化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我發覺好多野根本未夠知識去理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以真係愈讀愈覺得個課程好戇鳩"},{"pid":"a1b59ca7a30bf62fe1da5a8a89456a255bb9350b","tid":36743,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"諗番以前career嘅呀sir都叫我地腳踏實地揀科 ce廿分就唔好又gbus又medic咁 <br />\n以前梗係覺得呀sir睇我地唔起 而家諗番 佢哋都係講老實說話啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然舊制新制唔同 考ce係100%鬥勤力 al同dse係鬥天份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d2f15520d5780ad293220802dbf73bb7cd4660","tid":36743,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"根本唔洗理教畜D垃圾predicted grade<br />\n特別係比教畜pre死嘅同學仔<br />\n學校改卷好多時候有老師個人嘅定型評分標準 就算你表現好過拎開第一嘅人都未必會比得高分你<br />\nDSE先見真章 雖然一個小考試對人生唔係真係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8acfdfa3869f008ec5775108ace68e4356d7e7","tid":36743,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n年年打飛機d人一放完榜就會冇哂影架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43141670d6674cb440040bcfd3f2396f252ce2ac","tid":36743,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n年年打飛機d人一放完榜就會冇哂影架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e8cc288603fb02ae2c5409d3d0b5e0747f6c7e","tid":36743,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考前一大<br />\n考後三大<br />\n放榜八大<br />\n放jupas i大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">見過考完都覺後得自己入硬medic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果好似去咗讀職業治療</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為係朋友 教過佢幾次嘢 啲concept都頗亂<br />\n心諗有個5*都少少抆<br />\n又唔好意思開聲<br />\n<br />\n打緊飛機嘅人係永遠都唔會識得收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嗰個仲柒<br />\n佢喺校內(band 1尾)有頭10 aim medic<br />\n成級既同學連老師都吹捧到佢入硬medic, 當哂佢係學校唯一希望咁<br />\n不過佢份人幾好<br />\n佢最後個分連職治都入唔到, 入咗cu nursing<br />\n不過聽人講佢medic心未死, 想trans過去<br />\n聽完真心笑咗"},{"pid":"dd36d7414ffc525eaf04061da1471d71072b19d4","tid":36743,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n年年打飛機d人一放完榜就會冇哂影架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尤其舊時高登個啲dse討論post<br />\n個個講撚到自己aim25,6分"},{"pid":"cb564166cc13a2bc5a4b334adbe8467a9d883bcd","tid":36743,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本唔洗理教畜D垃圾predicted grade<br />\n特別係比教畜pre死嘅同學仔<br />\n學校改卷好多時候有老師個人嘅定型評分標準 就算你表現好過拎開第一嘅人都未必會比得高分你<br />\nDSE先見真章 雖然一個小考試對人生唔係真係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得教畜係衰印象 你唔好就一世都唔好<br />\n利申有科pre2 出嚟5<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma